Package: lliurex-inventory-agent
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, glpi-agent
Conflicts: fusioninstall (<< 1.0), fusioninventory-agent, fusioninventory-agent-task-network, fusioninventory-agent-task-deploy, fusioninventory-agent-task-esx
Description:  LliureX hardware and software inventory client
 The package installs required dependencies and configurations for the operation
 of GLPI agent within the GVA network of educational centres.
 .
 LliureX inventory management facilitates the support and maintenance of
 the educational centres' equipment.

Package: fusioninstall
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, lliurex-inventory-agent (= ${binary:Version})
Description: LliureX inventory agent dummy transitional package
 Force uninstallation of (old) fusioninventory-agent packages and installs
 new lliurex-inventory-agent package.
 This package can safely be removed after installation.
 .
 LliureX inventory management facilitates the support and maintenance of
 the educational centres' equipment.
 
